3
00:00:28,946 --> 00:00:31,615
<i>Try us. Please, from the start.</i>

4
00:00:33,867 --> 00:00:38,872
It started out small,
like a hand or a leg was in a different position.

5
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:41,542
Then its head was looking up
instead of down.

6
00:00:41,708 --> 00:00:44,753
And then one day, it was in
a completely different room.

7
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,463
It was moving around by itself.

8
00:00:46,630 --> 00:00:50,801
Ever think maybe somebody had a key
to your apartment and was playing a trick?

9
00:00:50,968 --> 00:00:52,636
That's exactly what we thought.

10
00:00:53,136 --> 00:00:55,806
But never once did we find any
sign or evidence of intrusion.

11
00:00:55,973 --> 00:00:58,725
And this all led you to believe
that the doll was possessed?

12
00:00:58,892 --> 00:01:00,269
Yes.

13
00:01:00,435 --> 00:01:04,147
Camilla got in touch with a medium.
We learned from her that a 7-year-old girl...

14
00:01:04,314 --> 00:01:07,234
...named Annabelle Higgins
had died in this apartment.

15
00:01:07,401 --> 00:01:11,113
She was lonely and took a liking
to my doll.

16
00:01:11,738 --> 00:01:13,657
All she wanted was to be friends.

17
00:01:13,865 --> 00:01:16,159
When we heard this,
we felt really sorry for her.

18
00:01:16,368 --> 00:01:18,996
I mean, we're nurses, we help people.

19
00:01:19,371 --> 00:01:20,497
So...

20
00:01:21,665 --> 00:01:24,126
...we gave her permission
to move into the doll.

21
00:01:24,293 --> 00:01:26,295
Wait, you did what?

22
00:01:26,670 --> 00:01:29,089
She wanted to live with us
by inhabiting the doll.

23
00:01:29,256 --> 00:01:30,424
We said yes.

24
00:01:30,591 --> 00:01:33,010
But then things got worse.

25
00:01:47,024 --> 00:01:48,358
God.

26
00:01:51,194 --> 00:01:54,364
<i>When we came home,
she was sitting in the hallway.</i>

27
00:01:54,531 --> 00:01:56,950
<i>But we had left her in the spare room.</i>

28
00:02:34,863 --> 00:02:36,948
Debbie! Debbie, wait!

29
00:03:51,815 --> 00:03:53,775
We are beyond terrified.

30
00:03:53,942 --> 00:03:57,904
We don't know what's going on
or what to do. Can you help us?

31
00:03:58,989 --> 00:04:00,532
Yes, we can.

32
00:04:00,949 --> 00:04:04,995
Now, firstly, there's no such thing
as Annabelle, and there never was.

33
00:04:05,162 --> 00:04:07,247
Ghosts don't possess such power.

34
00:04:07,414 --> 00:04:10,041
I think what we have here is something
extremely manipulative.

35
00:04:10,208 --> 00:04:12,169
It's something inhuman.

36
00:04:12,586 --> 00:04:14,838
It was a big mistake acknowledging this doll.

37
00:04:15,005 --> 00:04:17,174
And through that,
the inhuman spirit tricked you.

38
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:20,093
You gave it permission
to infest your lives.

39
00:04:20,594 --> 00:04:22,471
What's an inhuman spirit?

40
00:04:23,096 --> 00:04:26,516
It's something that's never walked
the earth in human form.

41
00:04:26,933 --> 00:04:28,810
It's something demonic.

42
00:04:32,647 --> 00:04:34,775
So the doll was never possessed?

43
00:04:34,941 --> 00:04:36,860
No, no, it was used as a conduit.

44
00:04:37,027 --> 00:04:39,362
It was moved around to give
the impression of possession.

45
00:04:39,529 --> 00:04:43,200
Demonic spirits don't possess things,
they possess people.

46
00:04:44,284 --> 00:04:46,453
It wanted to get inside of you.

47
00:04:55,796 --> 00:04:59,216
All right, that's good, Drew.
You can shut it down now.

48
00:05:00,884 --> 00:05:02,052
Hit the lights.

49
